Sedna/Rodimus:

Sedna started to react and move, soon she was full awake and roared 
and yelled while she tried to freed without succesfull. 

"Will you let us speak now?" said Rodimus with autority.

"WE HAVE NOT ANYTHING TO CHAT!!!!" snarled the femme.

"We have..."replied ROdimus"Who're you? and why are you controlling 
Nightlight...!!!"

"ASK HIM!!!!!" Motioned her head to Kenzo"Or your friend hasn't 
payed attention what I told him?"

Rodimus looked to Kenzo as if he expected a conrfirmation about what 
she was telling
